Basic instructions:
- apply org-icons.patch on the latest org-mode code
- in icons.el, set org-status-icons-default-directory to the appropriate directory
- load icons.el:
    M-x load-file RET icons.el RET
- switch to an org document
- re-fontify the buffer:
  M-x font-lock-fontify-buffer RET
- enjoy ;-)

Needless to say:
- the code is pre-alpha;
- any suggestion / contribution warmly welcome.
